snippet.title: Slice & Dice - Trailer [VR, HTC Vive, Oculus Rift]
snippet.description:
Trailer for Slice & Dice, a virtual reality puzzle game featuring realistic physics. Developed by VRotein, available for HTC Vive and Oculus Rift. You can find more information, as well as reviews and ratings here: https://vrgamecritic.com/game/slice-and-dice
